{"tid":677692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想溝架妺","createTime":"2018-05-25T12:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T18:11:55.000Z","uid":150079,"like":16,"dislike":185,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9075c6f033566c86a7c87f03ad1449e2c3bab6","tid":677692,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只適用於經常去日本人士或者留學生<br />\n此招適用於外國女仔<br />\n試過拎到韓國姐姐line<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先你要大膽係街問下路<br />\n方法一 問路法<br />\n十個有十個架妹都會答你，之後問邊到邊到點去，之後一路行一路傾，就問佢有冇去過香港，當傾傾吓佢警戒心放低左嘅時候，就問吓人攞Line（試過成功的）<br />\n方法二 Starbucks 法（適用於所有咖啡室）<br />\nStarbucks 搭訕法，去Starbucks買杯咖啡之後揀個靚靚架妹坐係隔離，拎部手機或者旅遊書出嚟，扮晒智障咁問人有咩好去,叫下人哋介紹下<br />\n方法三 佛系法<br />\n有時候啲日本妹好鍾意食雪糕，但係又唔帶紙巾，的到成地都係，比張濕紙巾之後傾吓計，得左，又或者日本有時落下雨日本妹又傻下傻下咁唔帶遮，遮下人也可能得呢？<br />\n你覺得有用就正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇用就負平<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟中文表達能力唔太好，請多關照，今日分享到此為止，ありがとう！"},{"pid":"0755c81b9a76dc39e86db8b82cbf0b8855ad9fcc","tid":677692,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"63f02e913604561ad03b143525f5ba62b0e25ecf","tid":677692,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:06:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d90a693fd838fca9588b9cdb7d1af35ce0d4a22","tid":677692,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"食過幾多個？"},{"pid":"963a64372a7ff4c4f66a3b95e13cddf66b5818df","tid":677692,"uid":61832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"aa13effa1dcd0a720da4f527cbf9a54163b54c5a","tid":677692,"uid":53798,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0